@startuml
title Diagrama de Componentes: Arquitectura del Sistema
package "Cliente" {
  [Next.js App] as Frontend
}
package "Servidor" {
  [FastAPI API] as API
  [pdf_service] as PDF
  [gemini_service] as Gemini
  [supabase_repository] as Repo
}
package "Servicios Externos" {
  [Supabase (DB, Auth, Storage)] as Supabase
  [Proveedor LLM (Gemini API)] as ExternalLLM
}

Frontend --> API: HTTPS (REST)
API --> PDF: llamada interna / tarea
API --> Gemini: adapter call
API --> Repo: llamadas DB
Repo --> Supabase: SQL / Storage
Gemini --> ExternalLLM: API HTTPS
@enduml
